{
  "stem": "8725.6",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And everybody, you train, you're doing, but with the evidence really come.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "There were sandwich laying here, the cigarettes there-- you know, it was spreaded it out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So I was trying to grab it like, trying to clean it up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "About, oh, two hours, or maybe more, the Major come.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He was drunk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He passed me by.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Well, I needed to know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I follow him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] wait for the decision of life or death.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He said, Irene, I cannot see you dead.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I want you to be mine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And willingly, I'll even help.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But you have to be mine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "There was nothing else I could do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "It was not easy, but it was small price to pay for so many lives.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Not only the lives in the villa, but the people in the forest, too.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I give myself to him, and I could not even tell my people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because how would they feel?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, that-- that only women.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He did not ask who else was there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was happy with me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were only innocent women.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And now that he knew, it was a little easier, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you know that the women-- you had Ida, and Franka, and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Heshu's wife-- I don't-- I have in a book.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I forgot.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were even to the point that he, when he-- it was now [NON-ENGLISH], because the Russians were now fighting the Germans.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the light were-- so I painted all the glass with the paint, you know, in the entry hall, and this.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the Major, a few times, he did not go down to the cellar, but he opened the door and called, Franka, Ida.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They made cookies for him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They made soup for him, when he was alone.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
